Name: Tacy Raino Ranta
Description:
Tacy was shot in the chest.

There was some debate at this time as to whether this was a hate-based murder, or simply a “random act of violence.”

Tacy Ranta was the spokesperson of It’s Time, Maryland! and cofounder of the Baltimore-based transgender support group Tran*Quility.
